## Repository structure
> Update these paths to match your repo layout.

Typical layout:
.
├── data/
│ ├── vignettes.csv # or .jsonl (one row/item per vignette)
│ └── README.md # data dictionary (optional)
├── prompts/
│ └── prompt_template.txt
├── scripts/
│ ├── run_benchmark.py # run inference + save outputs
│ └── analyze_results.py # aggregate counts, plots
├── results/
│ ├── model_outputs/ # raw outputs
│ └── summaries/ # tables/figures
├── paper/
│ └── 2026___AIME___ConflictResolution.pdf
└── README.md


