## Quickstart
> If your repo already has scripts/notebooks, replace the commands below with the real ones.

### 1) Create a Python environment
```bash
python -m venv .venv
# Windows:
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

python scripts/run_benchmark.py \
  --data data/vignettes.csv \
  --model gpt-4.1 \
  --temperature 0 \
  --protocol non_informed \
  --out results/model_outputs/gpt41_T0_non_informed.jsonl

python scripts/run_benchmark.py \
  --data data/vignettes.csv \
  --model gpt-4.1 \
  --temperature 0 \
  --protocol non_informed \
  --out results/model_outputs/gpt41_T0_non_informed.jsonl

